stories.title: Refreshed Twose looking forward to resuming battle
stories.summary: Roger Twose doesn't see a lack of match play as a problem as he leaves for Zimbabwe to join the New Zealand one-day cricket side

stories.title: If only it wasn't a whitewash
stories.summary:
Christchurch - The West Indian cricketers made a gallant attempt to
win the last match of their tour of New Zealand before 15 000
spectators at Jade Stadium on Tuesday (Monday night Caribbean time)
